MappableNode, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
public class DefaultTargetTreeNode
extends DefaultMappableTreeNode

This class extends the default mutable tree node as the tree node used to construct Target Tree for right-pane MetaData. One of primary reasons to have a distinct class is for differentiation purpose for future use of instanceof, for example.

Since:
CMTS v1.0
